## Verification Standard (Three-Layer AND)

Every claim requires ALL THREE proof artifacts:

### 1. OpenTelemetry Span (Execution Proof)
- Service name matching project
- Span name matching operation
- Timestamp with microsecond precision
- Attributes capturing key parameters
- Status field: "ok" or "error"

### 2. Test Assertion (Behavior Proof)
- Test file with `_test.{exs,go,rs}` extension
- Test name describing the claim
- Assertion capturing exact behavior
- Test PASSES (Green status)

### 3. Schema Conformance Proof (Weaver)
- `weaver registry check -r ./semconv/model -p ./semconv/policies/` exits 0
- Generated typed semconv constants used in test assertions

